<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>Info — Forsaken Tide</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css"><link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><text y='.9em' font-size='90'>⚓</text></svg>"></head>
<body>
<div class="bg"></div>
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo">FORSAKEN TIDE <span>info</span></div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/">Leaderboard</a>
    <a href="/info" class="active">Info</a>
    <% if (user) { %>
      <a href="/profile/<%= user.id %>">Profile</a>
      <% if (isAdmin) { %><a href="/admin">Admin</a><% } %>
      <div class="nav-user">
        <img class="nav-avatar" src="<%= user.avatar_url %>"><span class="nav-username"><%= user.username %></span>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Logout</a>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-gold">◆ Login with Discord</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="info-section">
  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="info-card-title">◆ ELO System</div>
    <div class="info-card-body">
      <p>Every player starts at <strong>0 ELO</strong>. ELO changes after each match using the modified Elo rating system.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>K-Factor:</strong> 8 — smaller changes for fairer progression</li>
        <li><strong>Minimum Change:</strong> ±1 ELO guaranteed per match, even if heavily favored</li>
        <li><strong>5-4 Score:</strong> If the loser scores 4 points in a FT5, the ELO change is <strong>halved</strong> (×0.5)</li>
        <li><strong>Formula:</strong> Higher ELO players gain less for beating lower ELO players; lower ELO players gain more for beating higher ELO players</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="info-card-title">◈ Ranks</div>
    <div class="info-card-body">
      <p>Your rank is determined by your current ELO:</p>
      <table class="info-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Rank</th><th>ELO Range</th><th>Fraction</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><span class="rank-badge">C</span></td><td>0 – 99</td><td><span class="frac-badge">F1</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><span class="rank-badge">B</span></td><td>100 – 249</td><td><span class="frac-badge">F1</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><span class="rank-badge">A</span></td><td>250 – 349</td><td><span class="frac-badge">F1</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><span class="rank-badge">S</span></td><td>350 – 400</td><td><span class="frac-badge">F2</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><span class="rank-badge">X</span></td><td>401 – 550</td><td><span class="frac-badge">F2</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><span class="rank-badge">Y</span></td><td>551 – 700</td><td><span class="frac-badge">F3</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td><span class="rank-badge">Z</span></td><td>701+</td><td><span class="frac-badge">F3</span></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="info-card-title">▣ Fractions</div>
    <div class="info-card-body">
      <p>Players are divided into <strong>3 fractions</strong> based on their rank/ELO to ensure fair matchmaking:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><span class="frac-badge">F1</span> <strong>Fraction 1</strong> — C, B, A ranks (0 – 349 ELO)</li>
        <li><span class="frac-badge">F2</span> <strong>Fraction 2</strong> — S, X ranks (350 – 550 ELO)</li>
        <li><span class="frac-badge">F3</span> <strong>Fraction 3</strong> — Y, Z ranks (551+ ELO)</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:12px;">Players can only fight opponents within their own fraction. This prevents high-rank players from farming low-rank players.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-card">
    <div class="info-card-title">⚔ Match Rules</div>
    <div class="info-card-body">
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Format:</strong> FT5 (first to 5 wins)</li>
        <li><strong>Same Fraction:</strong> Both players must be in the same F1/F2/F3</li>
        <li><strong>Max 3 per Week:</strong> You can only fight the same opponent <strong>3 times per week</strong> (Monday–Sunday)</li>
        <li><strong>Logging:</strong> Use <code>/ftlog</code> in Discord — mention both players, the winner, and the loser's score</li>
        <li><strong>Build:</strong> Set your build type (Normal / Skilled) and items on your profile page</li>
        <li><strong>Rank Roles:</strong> After each match, rank roles are automatically synced in Discord. Use <code>/ftsync</code> to manually re-sync</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<footer class="footer">Forsaken Tide Leaderboard &nbsp;|&nbsp; Built by ValTheOneAndOnly ❤️</footer>
